Name: Aureate Fried Rice
AttributesDescription: Reduces Wall Dash and Swimming STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 20% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A fried rice dish that every family in Jinzhou knows how to make. Each grain of rice is coated in a golden layer of egg yolk, symbolizing good fortune. It is often served during festive dinners in the mines, carrying the workers' wishes that their toil and frugality may bring about peace and prosperity.
